  <para>
    Using <classname>MinimumArea</classname> as the
    <varname>criterion</varname> in a <link
    linkend='RegisteredClass-Refine'>refinement</link> operation
    prevents any &elem; with an area less than the given
    <varname>threshold</varname> from being refined.  The
    <varname>threshold</varname> is specified either in units of the
    pixel size or in <link
    linkend='Section-Concepts-Microstructure-Coordinates'>physical</link>
    units, depending on the setting of the <varname>units</varname>
    parameter.
  </para>







